{
  "stem": "33.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I guess that was one of the reasons that we didn't believe that anything like this could happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were taken into the so-called disinfectation center, the showers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I was standing there waiting to get in, I turned around and I saw the men from our transport behind us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw my father there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not allowed to talk to  each other, but with the silent movement of his lips, he asked, where is your mother?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I shrugged, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know where my mother is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But again, the only way I can understand and I can explain the absolute, totally desperate look in his eyes when he didn't see my mother with me is that he was one of the few people who had an idea what is going to the left meant.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess this is not my imagination.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The prisoners that helped us off the train were some French, and some of German nationality.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father did speak both languages fluently, so somebody must have whispered something in his ears, because otherwise I wouldn't understand why he was so sad.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't, because I was going to see my mother later and my father was standing right behind me with a group of men.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were taken into these showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the first thing they did was, of course, we had to strip.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to take all our clothes off, which was the first traumatic experience, because your 18-year-old of 1944 is probably a lot younger than your 18-year-old of 1990s.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Walking among those staring prisoners and SS soldiers naked was pretty traumatic at that point.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Our heads were shaved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I do remember this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was with two of my-- three of my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
